  "slug": "vegan-wellington",
  "title": "Vegan Wellington",
  "subtitle": "Mushroom, chestnut, Puy lentil, and walnut filling in dairy-free puff pastry",
  "excerpt": "A vegan wellington replaces the cream cheese of a vegetarian version with Puy lentils, which give structure and an earthy depth. The method is the same as a standard wellington: cook the filling completely dry, cool it, wrap in dairy-free puff pastry, chill, and bake at high heat.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Contemporary British vegan cooking. Developed from the beef Wellington tradition and the wider vegetarian centrepiece tradition. Dairy-free puff pastry (made with vegetable fat) has been commercially available in British supermarkets since the 2000s.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The vegan wellington uses the same structure as the vegetarian version but with Puy lentils in place of cream cheese. The ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "lentil binding",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr5rjx0000ucv4cpk9awt1"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " gives a firmer, denser filling that slices cleanly and holds together without any dairy. The technique of cooking all moisture from the filling before assembly is even more important here: lentils add starch but they cannot compensate for a wet filling.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Use dairy-free puff pastry: most supermarket own-brand ready-rolled puff pastry is made with vegetable fat rather than butter and is suitable for vegans; check the packet. An ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "oat milk glaze",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr5rkm0001ucv4opxsgsuz"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " gives a good golden finish without eggs.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
